Request Verification:
- Verify requester identity and authorization
- Confirm manager or data owner approval is attached
- Review business justification for access

Access Requirements Analysis:
- Identify the specific system/resource requested
- Determine appropriate access level (read, write, admin)
- Check if access conflicts with separation of duties policies
- Verify user meets any compliance requirements

Existing Access Review:
- Check user's current access levels
- Identify if requested access is an upgrade or new
- Review access expiration requirements

Access Provisioning:
- Add user to appropriate security groups
- Configure permissions in target system
- Set access expiration date if temporary access
- Enable MFA if required for the resource

{% if access_type == 'vpn' %}
VPN-Specific Steps:
- Configure VPN client profile
- Assign VPN group membership
- Provide VPN connection instructions
{% endif %}

{% if access_type == 'shared_drive' %}
Shared Drive-Specific Steps:
- Add permissions to folder/drive
- Set inheritance options appropriately
- Verify access level (read/modify/full control)
{% endif %}

Verification and Documentation:
- Confirm user can access the requested resource
- Document access granted with approval reference
- Notify requester and approver of completion
- Update access review documentation
